INSERT INTO `forum_posts` VALUES(401, 1312, '2007-09-12 14:46:50', 're:Guild population.', 400, 55, '2007-09-12 14:46:50', 'I think we can start being more selective with our recruiting. It has been mentioned, but I believe we need to establish a standard. We have enough 60+ players that we should be able to say that we can put a level cap in place, possibly level 50.\r\nOne other thing that I was eyeing is that we have more than enough to do 1 kara run, and we should start looking at filling out classes for 2 kara runs. I know we haven\\''t been to kara as a guild yet, but that time is coming up very shortly. And there are going to be a lot of people getting left out each week. I propose that after we get our Kara A Team going and at least downing Moroes, we set up B Team which would comprise one or more of us that have been in Kara with the rest of the guild for experience and go from there... Just a thought.\r\n\r\nOn that note, we may need a few more recruits. I haven\\''t scrubbed the members graphs but I know we are lacking in certain classes.\r\n\r\nI propose we stop all recruiting at this time and see where we stand in 2 weeks time (26 Sept. 2007).\r\n\r\nDardel\r\n\r\n', 'no', '', 0);
