INSERT INTO `forum_posts` VALUES(421, 1335, '2007-09-25 08:41:06', 're:Members Pugging Kara', 420, 55, '2007-09-25 08:41:06', 'I kinda have to agree here. \r\nIf folks want to do stuff outside of the guild, they should think long and hard about why they joined.\r\nA counter-point to this whole discussion though is that this could easily cause a mass exodus. As several people have pointed out, they don\\''t want to be coerced or forced to do things that they don\\''t want to. And if folks feel like they are being pressured; they will leave and forming raids/groups might become  a serious problem.\r\nI have a few thoughts about this and a few other topics. But I will hold off as I want to gauge how this discussion will go and in which direction we steer things.', 'no', '', 0);
