INSERT INTO `forum_posts` VALUES(445, 1371, '2007-10-08 00:52:52', 're:Warrior: points in prot', 382, 47, '2007-10-08 00:52:52', 'Trust me....Last Stand has saved my ass many a time in raid/heroic/whatever.  It\\''s very handy.  With full kara buffs I sit at like 17.5k hp but when I blow Last Stand I\\''m at around 21k  It\\''s Very Helpful when coupled with Commanding Shout...another 1080 hp.  remember every little bit counts.  I almost didnt have a +20 stam food buff last time I tanked Prince.  well guees what.  when he hit phase 2 he knocked my hp down to 250.  that extra 200 health gave my healers enough time to toss me some health and I was back at it.  In short, every bit of hp is useful when tanking.  no matter what', 'no', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `forum_posts` VALUES(446, 1314, '2007-10-08 15:08:30', 're:Weighted Dice.', 442, 55, '2007-10-08 15:08:30', 'Question, Do you have to use your dkp in each raid? If I aquire say 20dkp afyer a boss is downed and nothing I want drops,then we call the raid to an end....do I carry that dkp for the next raid?\r\n\r\nAnd what about negative dpk? Will it be taken away for not showing up to a raid you signed up for(ie)? \r\n\r\nI think Alts should get the same dkp as mains. My reason for this is if you bring an alt to help the guild out you should be able to win an item. Example: Say Erry brings his warrior to help tank and a nice tanking piece drops the ot rolls as well; I think erry should be able to choose if he wants to spend his dkp on his alt rather than not having enough and losing the roll.\r\n\r\nI also have used a weighted dice dkp system it works well and helped us get people to want to raid which eventually lead WDA to become a rading guild. I like this system and I think it would make people want to get involved more.', 'no', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `forum_posts` VALUES(447, 1371, '2007-10-09 13:04:44', 're:Tanking gear:legs', 380, 47, '2007-10-09 13:04:44', 'Timewardens leggings ftw....just think about it...57 stam to start off with +3 gem slots...I put 3 +9 stam gems in mine and put a clefthide leg armor on it.  So in total I have 114 stam just on my legs.  As far as a ranged weapon goes....You might wanna consider farming the mats for Gyro-Balanced Khorium Destroyer.  Bottom line this is the best tanking ranged weapon outside of Black Temple.  I got mine and take solice in the fact that I wont have to look for an upgrade for a LOOOOONG time.  hehe.\r\n\r\nDeadman', 'no', '', 0);
