INSERT INTO `users` VALUES('Hase', '1', 'keres224', '', '', '', 'myhasegawa@gmail.com', '', '', '', '', 0, 1369, '', '', '2007-10-06 02:01:53', '', '', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '', 'apply', 'How old are you?\r\n\r\n21 years old \r\n\r\nWhat is your main characters talent spec?\r\n\r\n21/40/0 (willing to re-spec)\r\n\r\nHave you raided before?\r\n\r\nShort answer: No. I''ve been in PUGs for ZG and the world dragons but with little success. \r\n\r\nHave you been guilded before?\r\n\r\nYes. \r\n\r\nExplain:\r\n\r\nI''ve been in 2 guilds so far: Foamy Cult Alliance (from lvl 8 to 60) and Twist of Fate (from 60 to present) my 1st guild disbanded after the GM asked us to transfer to kilrogg. Most of us didn''t want to transfer. My second guild is real nice, but I''m looking to do end-game raiding in a serious way. I would like to see content before it becomes obsolete,  I''m a lore geek and I would love to experience those instances... (and I already missed the lvl 60 ones) \r\n\r\nOther Information:\r\n\r\nWell my character is currently in Ravencrest (PVE server) I would like to transfer because theres no much end-game progression in my server, we have low population, the people is really apathetic about the server in general (if u visit our forums you will see a lot of post about how the server sucks) and as much as I would like to help, the general apathy is just getting old to the point that is just not fun anymore to log in just to see people spamming in trade channel ''Ravenfail this, Ravenfail that'' \r\n\r\nAlso I''m Hispanic  and I live in Venezuela, sometimes i have a little trouble with making people understand me over vent (because my accent is not that great) but I have a decent english comprehension and I have little trouble understanding and listening to instructions. \r\n\r\nthis is the link to my armory http://www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Ravencrest&n=Krala I''m working to get better gear and find a nice spec, I already have the spellstrike patterns and as soon as I''m done with the spellfire set I''ll start working on that. (already have the primal nethers I need too) I know the gems I have in my gear are not the best ones... but as soon as I''m done crafting my sets ill get on that. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nWhat do you expect from the guild? \r\n\r\nMostly a friendly environment, where I can learn about end-game content. and I expect little drama and mature people. \r\n\r\nWhat can we expect from you?\r\n\r\nWell I''m a very helpful and nice person, also I''m very committed, i wont say i will go to a raid just to cancel a few hours before. I can take criticism and suggestions about spec/play style as long as they are exposed in a mature and positive way. I am not a loot whore/drama maker, but well i guess nobody will say "I''m a loot whore" in their app... =P you''ll see if you give me the chance to prove it =) \r\n\r\nI''m willing to raid up to 4 nights a week (4 hours each night) I''m a college student and well some specific weeks i wont be able to keep up with 4 nights a week (mostly on finals) but overall I can organize my time very well. \r\n\r\nI don''t know what else I can say... but if I''m missing something feel free to email me (or stop by Ravencrest and send me an in-game mail) asking whatever you want. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 0, 'I''m curious. -Terik\r\nI''m curious myself, i see some good things but see some personal "red flags" myself, I would be ok for trying it out - Lost\r\nI actually talked to this guy before he applied and I told him to fill out an app and told him we''d go from there. - Dardel\r\nhas he moved yet? -Terik\r\nI don''t know... I''ll go visit him on his server - Dardel', 'no', 8, 0);
